Package com.unvired.chyme.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Chart
    The Chart class provides an abstraction to represent tabular data graphically.
    ChymeAPI
    ChymeAPI provides the mechanism for a Bot to both receive messages from a Chyme conversation and respond to the user with a suitable message.
    Message
    The Message class provides an abstraction to represent a single message in a conversation between a User and a Bot.
    Recipient
    The Recipient class provides the Bot with an option to explicitly specify the recipients of a message in a conversation.
    SalesforceEvent
    The SalesforceEvent class is an abstraction of a business event or trigger generated in Salesforce.com An event is the creation, updating or deletion of a business entity in Salesforce.com
    SAPEvent
    The SAPEvent class is an abstraction of a business event or trigger generated in SAP An event in SAP could be the creation, updating or deletion of a business entity in SAP.
    WebEvent
    The WebEvent class is an abstraction of a business event or trigger generated in any system capable of http(s) communication.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Chart.ChartType
    ChartyType contains all supported chart types for use in Chyme
    ChymeAPI.ResultStatus
    Value to describe the overall status of the response from a Bot SUSSESS - Indicates that the Bot was able to handle the message successfully FAILURE - Indicates that there was functional error in processing the message RETRY - Indicates that there was a technical error in processing the message and that the user should retry the message
    Recipient.RecipientType
    RecipientType contains all supported recipient types for use in Chyme
